{"tid":272190,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚有痔瘡既朋友","createTime":"2017-06-05T15:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T04:37:02.000Z","uid":14007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"107c81e60dec3465835048677d6167e8158446cd","tid":272190,"uid":14007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:50:07.000Z","msg":"前排睇醫生 醫生話有痔瘡<br />\n比左啲藥我塞蘿柚 塞極都出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用左幾日藥都唔知係咪真係有效塞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生話隻藥有類固醇 唔可以用咁多<br />\n到而家大便都仲有痛 仲有血出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知點搞好 好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b5d13b4caa113963931ce182f7a93c9464001a","tid":272190,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"塞入啲"},{"pid":"475720f652dce13810cdc4335eb6457193b3f450","tid":272190,"uid":14007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:01:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>塞入啲</blockquote><br />\n已經博哂命塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係出返黎<br />\n再係咁出血 我好快貧血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadb1c9fdc8cc9044a08011ba91d243caa89ff3c","tid":272190,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>塞入啲</blockquote><br />\n已經博哂命塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係出返黎<br />\n再係咁出血 我好快貧血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你第幾期？"},{"pid":"